All your favourites in one place
《奇異博士2：失控多重宇宙》熱映中

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With a dizzying amount of content, Disney+ eloquently presents its massive catalog from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, and National Geographic for users to stream with wild abandon. And using GroupWatch, you and your friends can watch shows and movies synced in real-time—no matter where you are around the globe.
匯聚來自 Disney、Pixar、Marvel、星球大戰、國家地理等系列的大量節目，讓你盡情串流播放內容。使用 GroupWatch (同步觀看)，便可與朋友一起即時觀看影片。

The House of Mouse presents its massive catalogue from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, National Geographic and more to stream with wild abandon. And using GroupWatch, you can watch along with friends in real time.
ディズニー、ピクサー、マーベル、スター・ウォーズ™、ナショナルジオグラフィックなどの膨大なカタログを、思う存分配信で楽しめます。さらに、「GroupWatch」機能を使えば、友だちと一緒にリアルタイムで視聴できます。

The House of Mouse presents its massive catalogue from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, National Geographic, and more to stream with wild abandon. And using GroupWatch, you can follow along with friends in real time.
這款由迪士尼推出的的影音平台匯集了來自迪士尼、皮克斯、漫威、星際大戰和國家地理等知名品牌製作的海量內容。更棒的是，你還可以使用「GroupWatch」功能與朋友即時同步觀看節目。

Parcourez l’immense catalogue de Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, National Geographic et bien plus encore, et regardez tout à volonté. En plus, avec GroupWatch, vous pouvez organiser en temps réel des sessions de visionnage à plusieurs.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Disney+ is here! Start watching your favourite movies, TV series and more.
